    "Then Qwen and Llama3.1-8B-Instruct (Llama) (AI@Meta, 2024) are employed to generate predictions.",
    "We evaluate MetaTox from three perspectives: (1) Graph Evaluation, which provides qualitative and quantitative analysis on the constructed graphs; (2) Toxicity Prediction, where MetaTox is compared to baseline methods under both in-domain and cross-domain settings to evaluate effectiveness and robustness of MetaTox; (3) Case Studies, which offer in-depth analyses by guiding LLMs to output reasoning paths, providing insights into how MetaTox enhances interpretability and reasoning abilities.",
    "To validate the rationale behind our pipeline design, we have further devised an ablation study, the details of which can be found in Appendix B.",
    "For the constructed KG, to verify whether the triplets contain hate-related semantics and adhere to the required format, we conduct a manual evaluation.",
    "To conserve human resources, we sampled 100 triplets from each of the three constructed KGs."
